This need be fixed, otherwise this WAS 6.1 Symptom Catalog can not be use, unless message itself is changed. (By removing "]]&gt" string)
EMF is not escaping those characters when the resource is saved.

The editor cannot do anything about it, this needs to be fixed in the EMF resource save code.
Marius I'll assign this one to you for further investigation.
Alex feels this a model issue. Changing to Platform.Model component.

Praful please open a defect to Readme this problem in 4.2 if bug 143767 will not be fixed in 4.2 time frame.

The readme should mention this limitaton, the user should not enter ]]> in the UI or in the file directly.

*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of 143767 ***
